<br>
Empty eyes stare at the sun?burnt retina...lost in a horrific dreamscape of lost memories and nightmares.<br>
<br>
?all around him the field stretched on. Criss crossing trials of earth, plowed in a jumbled, crazy manner. Weaving in and out of each other. Always strait as an arrow, yet always moving.<br>
<br>
At his hip, a bag full of seed. Seeming to undulate without moving.<br>
<br>
He reached into the bag, grab a hand full to sow.<br>
<br>
Pain seared his skin. Burning his flesh black. Yet he did not flinch. Tossing the seed to the earth around him?tiny bursts of flame shimmering as they floated in slow motion the ground.<br>
<br>
Flames shot up all around him as the first flicker reached the ground. The barren landscape now filled with cascades of flame.<br>
<br>
?a harvest of fire?<br>
<br>
He spread his arms wide?screaming in agony as the tongues of heat licked his body.<br>
<br>
..rising off the ground in an updraft of shimmering heat?willing himself forward across the pyric field?<br>
<br>
His father stared to him ?face split with pride and hatred?<br>
<br>
Minz swung low over the old youth?raining acidic leaves of flame over him?laughing as the man twisted and fell in agony?breathing in deeply the sick sweet smell of burnt flesh?<br>
<br>
?a lyric sing song voice called out to him ? his mother?gazing at him alluringly...demure heavy lidded eyes full of lust?he swooped down cradling her in his arms?kissing her hungrily as her thin clothing burnt off?sailing to the sky in smoldering ashes.<br>
<br>
She giggled wickedly?wrapping her legs about her son's waist?grinding her hips to his pelvis?the son pressing himself to whence he came?crying out loudly?screaming in agony and ecstasy as the burst into flames from the inside out?<br>
<br>
?the world grew white hot?all definition lost?nothing but ?. searing? endless ecstasy?.<br>
<br>
Minz threw himself into it?<br>
<br>
giving himself up to the kiln of eternity<br>
<br>
<cough cough><br>
<br>
The water felt wrong in his mouth?shade? a quiet familiar voice?shapes and colors melding out of focus.<br>
<br>
He was alive?<br>
